Male: SZ 59.38-74.41, PR 7.47-9.53, FW 51.60-63.30, HW 54.21-66.23, HF 38.10- 48.26; Female: SZ 67.47, PR 7.8, FW 57.3, HW 60.61, HF 48.18, OV 26.64.
